About the bolt being focused or not.  I think Graccil is right.  I was using the EoLS to root mobs after the bolt left my hands.  It would start casting while the bolt was flying through the air.  So BAM the bolt lands then like 1 sec later he gets rooted.  I do that like 3-4 times then aggro kite until they are dead.  Thinking back now, I believe Graccil is right, all the unfocused bolts were when I was doing this.<br>
